    "body": "No, the distinction is on purpose, `cmd-m` is minified window. `cmd-a` is select all `ctrl-a` is go to beginning of line. This gives an extra modifier key on os x.\n\nIIUC, the handling is done [here](https://github.com/ipython/ipython/blob/master/IPython/html/static/notebook/js/keyboardmanager.js#L483-L507) where two instances of [this](https://github.com/ipython/ipython/blob/master/IPython/html/static/base/js/keyboard.js) are used.\n\nIt seem like [this line](https://github.com/ipython/ipython/blob/master/IPython/html/static/notebook/js/keyboardmanager.js#L12) can be remove.\n"
  },
